
----ADMIN CONSOLE----
(Step One) Within the "Travel Reimbursement" scope, (as the Courier Lead for Travel Reimbursement) submit a request.

(Step Two) Impersonate System Admin and search in the Navigator: Live Workflows > All Context.

(Step Three) Select the desired Task submitted by the Courier Lead.

(Step Four) Click on "Show Workflow."

