-----WORKFLOW EDITOR-----
(Step ) Go back to the Workflow Editor and add the following items from the Core Panel (See Workflow Example.JPG):
  -Approval User
  -Create Task
  -Set Values (Approved)
  -Set Values (Rejected)
 
(Step ) Go to the Workflow Actions tab and select "Validate Workflow."
 
(Step ) Publish it.
